Module app
Package app.entity_classes

Class Ingredients

java.lang.Object
app.entity_classes.Ingredients
public class Ingredients extends Object
Represents an ingredient used in the menu items of Rev's. Each ingredient is associated with a specific menu item through a menu ID and has properties like an ID, name, and the quantity of the ingredient available or required.
